$ sam -h
Split And Merge files (c) 2026 Ch1ffr3punk

Usage: sam [OPTIONS] [FILE]

Arguments:
  [FILE]

Options:
  -s, --split <SPLIT_SIZE_MIB>  Split file into chunks of X MiB
  -m, --merge <MERGE_FILES>...
  -o, --out <OUTPUT_PATH>       [default: .]
  -h, --help                    Print help
